11. Governance, Compliance, and Responsible Use
Even though the data is synthetic, governance matters:

## Synthetic Data Policy

CohGenT  is intended solely for generating synthetic, fictitious patient data for testing purposes. 
Do not enter, upload, or attempt to replicate any actual patient information, protected health information (PHI), or personally identifiable information (PII).
Any resemblance to real patients or individuals is purely coincidental. Users are solely responsible for ensuring compliance with applicable privacy laws and regulations, including HIPAA and other data protection requirements.


